                  <span class="date">May 15, 2025</span>
                  <span class="category">Product Update</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog-card">
              <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: #fff0e9;"></div>
              <div class="blog-card-content">
                <h2>5 Ways to Organize Your Reading List</h2>
                <p>Practical tips for keeping your saved links organized and making the most of your reading time.</p>
                <div class="blog-meta">
                  <span class="date">May 8, 2025</span>
                  <span class="category">Tips & Tricks</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog-card">
              <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: #f0f9e9;"></div>
              <div class="blog-card-content">
                <h2>The Future of Content Consumption</h2>
                <p>Our thoughts on how AI and personalization are changing the way we discover and consume online content.</p>
                <div class="blog-meta">
                  <span class="date">April 30, 2025</span>
                  <span class="category">Insights</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog-card">
              <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: #f5e9ff;"></div>
              <div class="blog-card-content">
                <h2>Customer Story: How Jane Transformed Her Research Process</h2>
                <p>Learn how one of our users is using lnksbot to streamline her academic research and stay on top of industry trends.</p>
                <div class="blog-meta">
                  <span class="date">April 22, 2025</span>
                  <span class="category">Customer Stories</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog-card">
              <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: #e9f0ff;"></div>
              <div class="blog-card-content">
                <h2>Behind the Scenes: How We Built Our Topic Clustering Algorithm</h2>
                <p>A technical deep dive into how we developed our topic clustering feature to help you see connections between your saved content.</p>
                <div class="blog-meta">
                  <span class="date">April 15, 2025</span>
                  <span class="category">Engineering</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="blog-card">
              <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: #ffe9f0;"></div>
              <div class="blog-card-content">
                <h2>Announcing Our New Mobile App</h2>
                <p>We're excited to launch our mobile app for iOS and Android, making it easier than ever to save and access your content on the go.</p>
                <div class="blog-meta">
                  <span class="date">April 8, 2025</span>
                  <span class="category">Product Update</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
